  2063                                  ;       Console Task
  2064                                  ;
  2065                                  ;       The only task defined in the kernel is the console task. This task consists of code, data, stack, and task state
  2066                                  ;       segments and a local descriptor table. The console task accepts and echos user keyboard input to the console
  2067                                  ;       screen and responds to user commands.
  2068                                  ;
  2069                                  ;=======================================================================================================================
